node.text:
Every social media guru tells you to create and share valuable content but never actually tells you exactly what valuable content is. 🤯😳 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Before we dive in click the link in our bio and make sure you’re on the waitlist for the ULTIMATE INSTAGRAM BLUEPRINT🎉 

Step by step guide on how to build a massive community organically on Instagram so you can Impact more lives with your message, product and services. 

This is not just about more followers it’s about knowing how to create a community of raving fans that will actually engage and ultimately buy from you. 🤑

node.text:
I get asked how to attract dedicated and engaged followers All. The. Time. Here are my best tips!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
[TAG your biz BESTIE in the comments] 👈
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Branded hashtag
A great way to create buzz and a collection of your best content! Create a dedicated, branded hashtag specifically for your business or product. Think along the lines of @lululemon’s #thesweatlife.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Industry-specific hashtags
Want to attract followers who are interested in what you’re offering? Use hashtags specific to your industry AND niche - what is your target audience browsing for specifically? Be really specific - you have a better chance of finding a truly interested audience.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Don’t be boring
Captions are your opportunity to grab users' attention and get them hooked! Move beyond a one-word caption - be funny, engaging, tell a story, and show yourself authentically.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Make the most of your bio URL
You only have one URL allowed in your bio so make it count! Try changing the link regularly or use a service that allows you to create a list of links (e.g. linktree, link in bio, etc).
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Develop your own style
Instagram has a huge audience so you want to stand out! Develop your own style (content style, colours, ‘voice’ - the whole kit and kaboodle), be unique, and be memorable.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Remember your calls to action!
Probably the biggest of them all is INCLUDE A CALL TO ACTION. ALWAYS. Ask your followers to take action on something. Do you want them to comment? Click your bio link? Tell you why they love this? Share a post with someone you know? Get your audience involved!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
@womanceomindset 👈
